{
  "stem": "6989.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't remember anything else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- I never really paid attention to foods too much it seems.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember ever being hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you know, being on a farm you're really not hungry, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I slept with Lena all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On some kind-- on a bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know which room or what.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then by that-- you know, slowly I sort of picked it up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And each time more and more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did speak Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, immediately when we went to the first house-- to the first-- to her mother and brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She-- nobody explained anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's just-- I was Mariusha and that's it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not like somebody sat down and explained things to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think we just knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You just know these things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At night.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She used to want to talk Jewish to me, and I didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was later on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the beginning, I don't think I talked too much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You just existed, you know, more or less.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remembered the fears, first of all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, through them not wanting to keep us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the fear-- I think I was very scared when we were walking with that police.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, when they took us into that little police station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] That's-- you know, the fear, I think, was always there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, since I left you sort of have fear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What helped me was that I wasn't with a stranger, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And because I really loved her, that I think helped me not to be as afraid as I would if it was a total stranger.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It never entered my mind.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
